OL,4,G1900FWild Scotland
OL,5,     GWildlife cameraman Gordon
OL,6,     GBuchanan explores his native Mull
OL,7,     Gand some of the nearby islands,
OL,8,     Gfilming otters, deer, puffins,
OL,9,     Gseals and a minke whale.
OL,10,G1915FThe Good Old Days
OL,11,     GLeonard Sachs presents the old-
OL,12,     Gtime music hall programme, from
OL,13,     Gthe City Varieties Theatre,
OL,14,     GLeeds. Guests include Ken Dodd,
OL,15,     GBarry Kent, Lyn Kennington, John
OL,16,     GBouchier and Saxburger.
OL,17,G2000FHetty Wainthropp Investigates
OL,18,     GWhen Hetty represents her
OL,19,     Gneighbour at a creditor's
OL,20,     Gmeeting, she is hired to find a
OL,21,     Gman who may have stolen from the
OL,22,     Gneighbour.
